						<summary>

						<p>On a slab set up near Sāhib Mohideen's mosque.</p>						

						<p>1215 A.D.</p>						

						<p>This is dated the cyclic year Yuva, Śrāvaṇa śu. 11, Sthiravāra. On palaeographical grounds the record may be assigned to the 13th century, in which case the details correspond to 1215 A.D., August 7. The weekday was Friday.</p>						

						<p>It records the death by <hi rend="italic">samādhi</hi> of the pontiff Māghanandi.</p>						

						</summary>
